<!-- SECTIONS -->

<section class="section-padding" style="margin-bottom: -400px;">
  <div class="container">
  
      <div class="row m1">
        <div class="col-lg-6 ">
          <div class=" wow fadeInDown "> <img src="img/security_1.png"  height="70px" alt="security icon">
            <h4> End 2 End Encryption</h4>
            <p>All your messages and files are encrypted with 256-bit AES before they leave your device and are decrypted only when they reach their recipients. This means your data is encrypted both in transit and on our servers. </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-6">
          <div class=" wow fadeInDown "> <img src="img/security_2.png"  height="70px" alt="security icon">
            <h4>Zero Knowledge Solution</h4>
            <p>All encryption keys are generated by the client and secured by your password, while they are on our servers. We also utilize RSA public key cryptography to securely pass keys to recipients. This means your raw encryption keys are never exposed to anyone, and even Zebu canâ€™t read them.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="row m1">
        <div class="col-lg-6">
          <div class=" wow fadeInDown "> <img src="img/security_3.png"  height="70px" alt="security icon">
            <h4> Unique Keys for Discussions</h4>
            <p>Each Discussion and chat are protected by a unique key, so team members only have keys to channels they have access to. This means, a security breach in one team/department will never compromise data from other departments.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-6 ">
          <div class=" wow fadeInDown "> <img src="img/security_4.png"  height="70px" alt="security icon">
            <h4> External Connections</h4>
            <p>Users within one Zebu organization can communicate with contacts in another with the use of external connections. This allows users to communicate with people from different organizations while still maintaining a high level of security and privacy.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="row m1">
        <div class="col-lg-6 ">
          <div class=" wow fadeInDown "> <img src="img/security_5.png"  height="70px" alt="security icon">
            <h4> Per-Message & Per-File Encryption</h4>
            <p>Zebu encrypts all of your messages and files with a different encryption key, ensuring the maximum possible protection of your data. This makes sharing messages and files both easy and secure.



 </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-6">
          <div class=" wow fadeInDown "> <img src="img/security_6.png"  height="70px" alt="security icon">
            <h4>Forward and Backward Security</h4>
            <p>Each message and file is encrypted with a new key. Breaking 1 key would take millions of years and so a compromise is both unlikely, and has minimal impact on overall security. </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="row m1">
        <div class="col-lg-6">
          <div class=" wow fadeInDown "> <img src="img/security_7.png"  height="70px" alt="security icon">
            <h4>Ease of Use</h4>
            <p>Zebu is designed with both security and usability in mind. You can access all your files and messages from any browser or device without having to pre-register or synchronize devices. Unlike other platforms you can still access conversation history to get to the information you need.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-6 ">
          <div class=" wow fadeInDown "> <img src="img/security_8.png"  height="70px" alt="security icon">
            <h4> Clear Business Model</h4>
            <p>We are not in the business of selling, mining and sharing user data. Zebu is a service that makes its money on monthly subscriptions.  </p>
          </div>
        </div>
		     

      
 
    </div>
	   <img class="img-responsive sheild" src="img/zebee-sheild.png" alt="strong safe sheild with zebee"> 
    
  </div>
</section>
